[[File:Wall_tower_lookout.png|right]]The '''Lookout Tower''' is a building in [[Lord of Ultima]]. It enables incoming attacks to be seen sooner. (Time without Lookout Tower: 1 Hour). Increases the Defensive Value of a limited amount of Scouts by 100%. If there are not enough Scouts in the city, 2 city guards can take each slot and gain the same bonus. Lookout Towers don't count towards a city's building number limit.

'''Requirements:''' [[Town Hall]] Level 2

